00:20:18.482 --> 00:20:20.487
what they're talking about.
even if it's mean.

487
00:20:20.572 --> 00:20:23.560
Right. but didn't you. like.
go into god-mode and fight mom?

488
00:20:23.644 --> 00:20:25.708
Love is the only power
that matters. Morty.

489
00:20:25.793 --> 00:20:28.170
No. you had actual power.
and you did jack shit.

490
00:20:28.254 --> 00:20:29.353
That was a divine staff.

491
00:20:29.438 --> 00:20:31.245
You could've cured cancer
or raised the dead.

492
00:20:31.330 --> 00:20:33.906
- Instead you made bugs.
- Well. I was impressed. Dad.

493
00:20:33.991 --> 00:20:36.239
He saved my life.
no thanks to you.

494
00:20:38.839 --> 00:20:40.406
Your kids got high
on alien mist

495
00:20:40.491 --> 00:20:41.910
and drove the ship
into that Zeus guy's head.

496
00:20:41.994 --> 00:20:43.200
- Basically murdered him.
- Grandpa!

497
00:20:43.284 --> 00:20:44.170
- What the hell?!
- Come on! What? - You did.

498
00:20:44.255 --> 00:20:45.733
I mean. not to cast
the first stone.

499
00:20:45.818 --> 00:20:48.371
but. Beth and Jerry. pretty
terrible parenting on your part.

500
00:20:48.474 --> 00:20:50.120
Did you know Summer huffed
a K-Zax Array?

501
00:20:50.204 --> 00:20:51.590
She basically
smoked "The Ring."

502
00:20:51.674 --> 00:20:53.180
Most pilots die
after three days.

503
00:20:53.265 --> 00:20:54.720
And Morty. the fucking moron.
he thought

504
00:20:54.804 --> 00:20:56.530
the ship worked
like a game controller.

505
00:20:56.614 --> 00:20:58.460
What in the Disney
Channel fuck is that?

506
00:20:58.544 --> 00:21:00.209
Maybe help him with
homework next time.

507
00:21:00.294 --> 00:21:01.658
He's clearly
crying for help.

508
00:21:02.093 --> 00:21:04.093
<font color=#ffc30f>Sync corrections</font> by <font color=#00FF00>srjanapala</font>

509
00:21:33.227 --> 00:21:36.284
<i>Planets Only.
Planets Only. Planets Only.</i>

510
00:21:36.369 --> 00:21:39.322
<i>Entire systems of steamy.
lush globes</i>

511
00:21:39.407 --> 00:21:42.244
<i>and barely habitable
celestial objects</i>

512
00:21:42.329 --> 00:21:44.803
<i>are drifting through
the void just for you.</i>

513
00:21:44.888 --> 00:21:46.801
<i>- Planets Only.
- Let's terraform.</i>

514
00:21:46.886 --> 00:21:49.832
<i>- Or colonize me as I am.
- Planets Only.</i>

515
00:21:49.917 --> 00:21:52.380
<i>Oops. there's a hole
in my ozone.</i>

516
00:21:52.464 --> 00:21:53.920
<i>I didn't put it there.
Did you?</i>

517
00:21:54.004 --> 00:21:57.460
<i>I can't fill it by myself.
I'm not smart enough.</i>

518
00:21:57.544 --> 00:22:00.190
<i>Young. dumb.
and orbiting the sun.</i>

519
00:22:00.274 --> 00:22:03.330
<i>The greenhouse is in full effect
at Planets Only.</i>

520
00:22:03.414 --> 00:22:06.217
<i>Oh. I want you to split my
Pangea into distinct continents.</i>

521
00:22:06.301 --> 00:22:08.870
<i>I don't have hydrostatic
equilibrium yet.</i>

522
00:22:08.954 --> 00:22:10.701
<i>Is that something
you can learn?</i>

523
00:22:10.793 --> 00:22:12.129
<i>You get the idea.</i>

524
00:22:13.616 --> 00:22:14.643
Phew!

525
00:22:14.729 --> 00:22:16.610
I was watching over your
shoulder for a full minute.

526
00:22:16.694 --> 00:22:18.069
So? I was watching because
it's funny.

527
00:22:18.153 --> 00:22:19.658
It's... It's... They... They...
They're planets.

528
00:22:19.742 --> 00:22:21.795
but they're sexy.
It's a comedic premise.

529
00:22:21.880 --> 00:22:24.550
- Yeah.
- <i>Planets Only.</i>

530
00:22:24.634 --> 00:22:26.074
<i>Planets Only.</i>
